###
# University Assist API Examples - Universities
# 
# Base URL: https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1
# 
# Replace {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY} with your actual key
# Replace {JWT_TOKEN} with valid JWT for authenticated requests
###

### List all universities
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/universities
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Universities with city information
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/universities?select=id,name,slug,website,cities(name,slug)
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Universities in specific city
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/universities?select=id,name,slug,website,type,control_type&city=eq.Berlin
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Universities by city ID
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/universities?select=*,cities(name)&city_id=eq.{city-uuid-here}
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Search universities by name
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/universities?select=id,name,slug,city,website&name=ilike.*Technical*
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Universities with programs count
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/universities?select=id,name,slug,city,programs(count)
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Public universities only
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/universities?select=id,name,slug,city,control_type&control_type=eq.public
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Universities with location data
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/universities?select=id,name,slug,lat,lng,city&lat=not.is.null&lng=not.is.null
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Universities ordered by ranking
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/universities?select=id,name,slug,city,ranking&order=ranking.asc
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get specific university by slug
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/universities?select=*,cities(name,slug)&slug=eq.tu-berlin
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Universities with pagination
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/universities?select=id,name,slug,city&limit=10&offset=0&order=name.asc
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Universities by type (e.g., Technical University)
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/universities?select=id,name,slug,city,type&type=ilike.*University*
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Universities with complete profile data
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/universities?select=*,cities(name,slug,state),programs(count)&limit=5
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json